graph TD
    A[Start: Take Picture] --> B{Camera Available?}
    B -- Yes --> C[Clear Camera Buffer]
    B -- No --> D[Try to Start Camera]
    D --> E{Camera Started?}
    E -- Yes --> C
    E -- No --> F[Error: Camera Failed]
    C --> G[Capture Photo]
    G --> H{Photo Captured?}
    H -- Yes --> I[Convert to Image Format]
    H -- No --> J[Retry Capture]
    J --> K{Max Retries Reached?}
    K -- No --> G
    K -- Yes --> F
    I --> L[Return Photo]
    F --> M[End: Failed]
    L --> N[End: Success]